  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In current set of synced data among the data that is not being updated right after initial sync are:\r\n- account currency\r\n- \"Accept chats from\" setting value\r\n- \"See profile pictures from\" setting value\r\n- \"Show profile pictures to\" setting value\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n\r\n1. Create multiaccount on Device 1 \r\n2. On Device 1 generate the following data that will be synced: \r\n- Create community\r\n- Create a new channel in community\r\n- Send some message in newly created community channel\r\n- Add profile picture\r\n- Set Accept chats from setting value to Contacts\r\n- Set See profile pictures from setting to Everyone\r\n- Set Show profile pictures to to None\r\n- Add watch only account\r\n- Change account currency (for example set value to AFN)\r\n- Start 1-1 chat with any user, add this user to contacts\r\n- Start a group chat with newly added contact\r\n\r\n**Below video demonstrates the process of generating the above listed data:** \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/178249431-1d71c6ff-0573-4787-b557-f2456ff06c62.mp4\r\n\r\n3. Restore account on Device 2\r\n4. Pair Device 1 and Device 2\r\n5. Tap Sync button on Device 1\r\n6. Check if all synced data has appeared on Device 2 \r\n\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** \r\nfollowing values have not been updated on Device 2 after sync:\r\n- \"Accept chats from\" setting value\r\n- \"See profile pictures from\" setting value\r\n- \"Show profile pictures to\" setting value\r\n- account currency\r\n\r\nValues are being updated only after performing re-login on Device 2\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/178250562-4cdbae35-7c9f-4575-afa3-5f2bcfdfeec3.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** all data has been updated on paired Device 2 right after performing sync.\r\n\r\n[IOS_geth.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/9083371/IOS_geth.log)\r\n[Android_geth.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/9083373/Android_geth.log)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n**- Bug appeared since nightly from July 8.** \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n**Note for QA team:** current issue causes the need to relogin after syncing in group of tests TestPairingSyncMediumMultipleDevicesMerged. Relogin should be removed after fix of this issue. \r\n",
